<item>
            <title>[HBASE-13404] Add/Refactor vint and vlong related functions in Bytes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-13404</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bytes has these 4 functions for a lot of data types, might make sense to add missing ones/fix existing ones related to vint and vlong.&lt;br/&gt;
1) read X from byte[]&lt;br/&gt;
2) read X from offset in byte[]&lt;br/&gt;
3) put X in byte[] at a given offset&lt;br/&gt;
4) return byte[] for X&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also add tests for these new/changed functions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
