                                        <comments>
                            <comment id="14395140" author="stack" created="Fri, 3 Apr 2015 21:56:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=apeksharma&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;apeksharma&quot;&gt;inactive&lt;/a&gt; Is this a good idea? The Bytes vint stuff is only used in a few places, the vint implementation is not very good (hadoop) and not the same as pb, and even where we do use vints, I think its fair to say we now regret it (at least for mvcc on Cell).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14395438" author="appy" created="Sat, 4 Apr 2015 01:07:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@stack I just thought adding missing fns for vint/vlong would be good idea and will make Bytes more complete library (realized while fixing &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6919&quot; title=&quot;Remove unnecessary throws IOException from Bytes.readVLong&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-6919&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-6919&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). Now that you have given me context, i guess this change won&apos;t be very useful.&lt;br/&gt;
Although I already have the patch ready, I&apos;ll leave the call to continue/abort to you (attaching patch for your reference).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14395442" author="appy" created="Sat, 4 Apr 2015 01:17:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes in patch&lt;br/&gt;
VInt functions added&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; readAsVInt(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[] buffer)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; readAsVInt(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[] buffer, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; offset)  &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// deprecated bytesToVint
&lt;/span&gt;putAsVInt(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[] buffer, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; offset, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; vint)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt; [] vintToBytes(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; vint)  &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// deprecated vintToBytes(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; vint)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VLong functions added&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; readAsVLong(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt; []  bytes)
putAsVLong((&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[] buffer, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; offset, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; vlong)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt; [] vlongToBytes(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; vlong)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+ some tests&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
